title: Screamin' Jay Hawkins - I put a spell on you - The singles 1954-
description:
Great anthology including Screamin' Jay Hawkins hit single version of 'I Put A Spell On You' which inspired generations of great artists

Tracks 1 to 4: possibly accompained by Wynonie Harris's band. Recorded at New York, September 1953.
Tracks 5 and 6: Recorded at New York, January 1955.
Tracks 7 to 10: Recorded at New York, 11 May 1955.
Track 11 and 12: Recorded at New York, 12 September 1956.
Track 13 and 14: Recorded at New York, 13 February 1957.
Track 15 and 16: Recorded at New York, 6 May 1957.
Tracks 5 - 14: Jay Hawkins With Leroy Kirkland Orchestra
